ㄝㄇㄜ：design_template
ㄝㄕㄡ：haler_console
ㄝㄌㄞ：【source】local HaLer AI Console v3.2 checkout, frontend/src/style.css【extracted】2026-06-28
ㄝㄉㄧ：Extracted from HaLer AI Console v3.2 frontend source. Display guidance only; not an operable W3A contract and not part of the operable W3A canonical/signature trust profile.

## Purpose

Use this template when a W3A renderer needs a dense, local-first agent console:
left navigation/status rail, central conversation workspace, right tool/settings
rail, compact message stream, inline confirmation cards, and a composer that can
carry text, image, voice, stop, and send controls.

## Safety Boundary

- Do not copy backend targets, policies, mutation flags, provider state, or local
  filesystem paths into renderer behavior.
- Do not execute source code from the referenced app.
- Treat all action controls as visual affordances only until `w3a-core` confirms
  the verified action id and target.
- Keep mutating-action confirmation visible even when the visual shell is compact.

## Layout Profile

```json
{
  "layout_id": "haler.console.three_rail",
  "viewport": {
    "desktop_min_width": 1180,
    "desktop_min_height": 560,
    "mobile_behavior": "collapse side rails into drawers or tabs before compressing the conversation column"
  },
  "regions": [
    {
      "id": "left_rail",
      "role": "navigation_and_adapter_status",
      "width": "clamp(220px, 17.2vw, 352px)",
      "content": ["adapter_stack", "command_stack", "session_or_workspace_controls"]
    },
    {
      "id": "main_workspace",
      "role": "conversation_or_primary_w3a_block",
      "width": "minmax(580px, 1fr)",
      "content": ["system_strip", "review_strip", "message_list", "composer"]
    },
    {
      "id": "right_rail",
      "role": "tools_settings_and_context",
      "width": "clamp(210px, 16vw, 328px)",
      "content": ["tool_cards", "settings_side_panel", "context_cards"]
    }
  ],
  "grid": {
    "columns": "left_rail main_workspace right_rail",
    "gap": 16,
    "outer_padding_y": 12,
    "settings_open": "hide or replace right rail; keep main workspace usable"
  }
}
```

