## Component Roles

```json
{
  "adapter_button": {
    "shape": "compact horizontal button with icon cell, label, source badge, status dot",
    "states": ["online", "offline", "degraded", "active"],
    "notes": "labels truncate; status dot is fixed-size and never shifts layout"
  },
  "panel": {
    "shape": "rounded 10px container with 1px translucent border",
    "behavior": "scroll internally; never let side panels cover the composer"
  },
  "system_strip": {
    "shape": "short high-contrast status bar above conversation",
    "height": "about 35px",
    "use_for": ["runtime status", "trust badge", "draft/test warning"]
  },
  "message_list": {
    "shape": "vertical stack with 12px gaps and internal scrolling",
    "ai_message": "left aligned, max width 96%",
    "user_message": "right aligned, max width min(78%, 680px)",
    "active_message": "reveals action buttons without resizing text content",
    "text_policy": "pre-wrap, long words break anywhere, compact previews can expand"
  },
  "search_summary_card": {
    "shape": "inline draggable card with icon, title, metadata, count chip",
    "tone": "cyan content on dark teal, highlighted by warm outline"
  },
  "inline_review_card": {
    "shape": "bordered card inside the message stream",
    "use_for": ["high risk confirmation", "permission diff", "tool operation review"],
    "actions": "right aligned, wrap on small screens"
  },
  "composer": {
    "layout": "three icon buttons plus flexible input",
    "controls": ["attach", "stop", "voice", "textarea", "send"],
    "send_button": "magenta gradient, absolute inside input area",
    "confirmation": "amber confirm bubble above composer before mutating operation",
    "attachments": "image thumbnails occupy stable slots before text"
  },
  "settings_side_panel": {
    "shape": "scrollable side panel with title row, grouped controls, compact cards",
    "motion": "short drop-in; must be disabled under reduced motion"
  },
  "onboarding_language_strip": {
    "shape": "visible same-page language choice with pill buttons",
    "notes": "keep language selection visible instead of hiding it in a CLI-only setup"
  },
  "action_role_slots": {
    "primary_submit": {
      "match": "verified W3A action that submits the current composer/form or starts the main user-confirmed flow",
      "component": "composer.send_button",
      "style": "compact magenta gradient button inside or beside the input; icon-forward, high contrast, fixed size",
      "fallback": "derive a same-size high-emphasis composer button from the send color token; do not create a feature"
    },
    "secondary_action": {
      "match": "verified secondary action, close/back action, or low-risk helper action",
      "component": "small panel or message-row icon/text button",
      "style": "dark surface button with warm text, subtle border, and visible focus ring"
    },
    "compact_icon_action": {
      "match": "verified action that is best exposed as a small repeated toolbar or row affordance",
      "component": "composer icon button or active_message row button",
      "style": "fixed square icon cell; label appears in tooltip or expanded state"
    },
    "navigation_or_filter": {
      "match": "display navigation, search, filter, or tab-like control",
      "component": "adapter_button, toolbar search control, or onboarding pill",
      "style": "compact rounded control with status dot or badge when state is verified"
    },
    "destructive_confirm": {
      "match": "verified destructive, irreversible, or high-risk mutating action that already requires confirmation",
      "component": "inline_review_card action area",
      "style": "amber confirmation surface with danger accent on the final button",
      "notes": "visual treatment only; confirmation and target still come from w3a-core"
    }
  }
}
```

## W3A Block Mapping

```json
{
  "ㄆㄤ": "render as message_list plus composer when submit action exists",
  "ㄗㄞ": "render as dense stacked rows or table-like cards",
  "ㄔㄠ": "render as composer/form surface pinned near the related data block",
  "ㄙㄞ": "render as compact toolbar search control above list/message area",
  "ㄉㄟ": "render as right-rail context card or inline review card",
  "ㄇㄢ": "render as safe plain text in a message row or simple panel"
}
```

## Interaction Guidance

- Use icon buttons for attach, stop, voice, settings, copy, delete, and expand.
- Show unfamiliar icons with tooltips.
- Keep action buttons hidden until row focus/active state when the list is dense.
- Use compact three-line previews for long generated/search-summary text, with a
  localized expand/collapse control.
- Put destructive or mutating confirmations inline near the composer or affected
  message, not in a detached decorative panel.
- Do not nest UI cards inside other cards; use panels for main regions and cards
  only for individual repeated items, review prompts, or modal content.

## Source Notes

- Durable CSS source: local HaLer AI Console v3.2 checkout,
  `frontend/src/style.css`.
- Generated CSS was intentionally not used as source truth.
- Key local selectors used for extraction: `.console-shell`, `.left-panel`,
  `.conversation-panel`, `.right-panel`, `.message-list`, `.message-row`,
  `.message-ai`, `.message-user`, `.composer`, `.input-wrap`,
  `.send-btn`, `.settings-side-panel`, `.onboarding-language-strip`.

